    <item>
      <title>日本首相石破茂表示当选首相后不会实施免税储蓄政策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/japan-s-ishiba-says-won-t-hit-tax-free-savings-if-elected-pm</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本前防卫大臣石破茂在执政党领袖竞选活动前回答提问时表示，他不会对免税储蓄计划征税，该竞选活动旨在决定下一任首相。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/japan-s-ishiba-says-won-t-hit-tax-free-savings-if-elected-pm</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 08:14:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国特使称中国减排是实现世界气候目标的关键</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/german-envoy-says-china-emissions-are-key-to-world-climate-goal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国首席气候特使表示，中国控制排放的承诺可能决定世界是否能够实现将全球变暖限制在比工业化前平均水平高 1.5 摄氏度的目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-06/german-envoy-says-china-emissions-are-key-to-world-climate-goal</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 07:50:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
